1. "*Nećeš* li se odazvati na poziv?" (Won't you respond to the invitation?)
2. "Šta god da ti kažem, *nećeš* to prihvatiti." (Whatever I tell you, you won't accept it.)
3. "Nikada *nećeš* znati šta je najbolje za tebe." (You will never know what is best for you.)
4. "Videćeš da *nećeš* požaliti što si prihvatio." (You will see that you won't regret accepting it.)
5. "Ako čekiraš, *nećeš* uspeti da stigneš na vreme." (If you take the check, you won't manage to arrive on time.)